                <h2 class="blue section-title">Find unique &  traditional guided tours</h2>

                <p>We hand-pick private tours with unique elements  that you can’t find elsewhere. We also select a number of high-quality tours to  traditional landmarks for first-time visitors, and travellers with a limited  time frame.</p>

                <p>Don’t share your experiences with busloads of  tourists. Our private and small group tours allow you to experience the world  with a local by your side without compromising your enjoyment.</p>

                <p>We have a wide range of tours covering everything  from sports & activities, culture, history, architecture, photography to  cooking and much more.</p>
                
                <p>We negotiate the best prices so you can enjoy  high-quality tours at competitive prices.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
                <img src="/images/whykootour/icon-for-why-kootour.png" />
            </div>
        </div> <!-- /.row -->

        <hr class="blue">

        <div class="align-item row section" id="section-2">
            <div class="hidden-xs hidden-sm col-md-4 col-lg-4">
                    <img src="/images/whykootour/icon_booktours.png" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-8">
                <h2 class="section-title blue">Book your tour</h2>

                <p>We take the hassle out of travel. Find high quality  guides who will meet you at your hotel, or pick you up from the airport to  deliver a seamless experience.</p>
                
                <p>Our instant book feature means that your plans  are confirmed straight away. Your tour is booked as soon as the payment has  been received.</p>
                
                <p>Customize your tour with our range of inbuilt  customizable options.</p>

                <p>Your guide will be in touch with any further  information and to provide useful recommendations about your tour.</p>
            </div>
