                <h2 class="section-title blue">Safe & secure payment solutions</h2>

                <p>We use Stripe (link) to safely receive payments.  No card details are held and the transfer is encrypted.  The payment is held until after the tour concludes  for peace of mind and in the rare case that refunds are required.</p>
                
                <p>No cash is exchanged with the tour guide - so no  need to carry large amounts of cash or encounter any uncomfortable situations over  transactions.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
                    <img  src="/images/whykootour/icon_payment solutions.png" />
            </div>
        </div> <!-- /.row -->

